🗃️ Table User
- id (INT, PK)
- email (VARCHAR)
- password (VARCHAR)  // bcrypt

🗃️ Table Quiz
- id (INT, PK)
- titre (VARCHAR)

🗃️ Table Question
- id (INT, PK)
- texte (TEXT)
- quiz_id (INT, FK -> Quiz.id)

🗃️ Table Answer
- id (INT, PK)
- texte (VARCHAR)
- is_correct (BOOLEAN)
- question_id (INT, FK -> Question.id)
